msgid ""
":icon:`fa-undo` :guilabel:`Recall`: Undo the most recent order stage move. "
"This is only possible if this move was made on the selected stage."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-undo` :guilabel:`Cofnij`: Cofnij ostatnie przesunięcie etapu "
"zamówienia. Jest to możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy to przesunięcie zostało "
"wykonane na wybranym etapie."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:113
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Done`: Delete all completed orders in the last "
"stage at once."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Gotowe`: Usuń wszystkie zakończone zamówienia z "
"ostatniego etapu jednocześnie."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:114
