#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:149
msgid ""
"Stages, i.e., the status such as `To prepare`, `Ready`, etc., highlighted in "
"the defined color (only shown when :guilabel:`All` orders are displayed)."
msgstr ""
"Etapy, tj. status taki jak `Do przygotowania`, `Gotowe` itp., podświetlone "
"zdefiniowanym kolorem (wyświetlane tylko wtedy, gdy pokazywane "
"są :guilabel:`Wszystkie` zamówienia)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:151
msgid ""
