msgstr ""
"Wybierz produkt do zważenia na ekranie zamówienia lub zeskanuj jego kod "
"kreskowy."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:89
msgid ""
"Place the product on the scale and wait for the weight to be displayed in "
