#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:90
msgid "Once the weight is determined, the price is automatically computed."
msgstr "Po ustaleniu wagi cena jest automatycznie obliczana."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:91
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Order` :icon:`fa-angle-double-right` to add the product to "
