#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/worldline.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ offers payment solutions "
"through :doc:`payment terminals <../terminals>` to handle customer "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ oferuje rozwiązania płatnicze "
"poprzez :doc:`terminale płatnicze <../terminals>`, aby obsługiwać transakcje "
"klientów."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/worldline.rst:9
msgid ""
"Connecting a Worldline payment terminal to Odoo requires an :doc:`IoT system "
"</applications/general/iot/connect>`."
msgstr ""
"Połączenie terminala płatniczego Worldline z Odoo wymaga :doc:`systemu IoT </"
"applications/general/iot/connect>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/worldline.rst:11
msgid ""
"Worldline is only available in **Belgium**, **the Netherlands**, and "
"**Luxembourg** with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Worldline jest dostępny tylko w **Belgii**, **Holandii** i **Luksemburgu** z "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/worldline.rst:12
msgid ""
"Odoo is compatible with Worldline terminals that use the CTEP protocol "
