#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/worldline.rst:82
msgid ""
"To prevent connection loss, set a fixed IP address on the IoT Box’s router "
"or :ref:`restart the virtual IoT server <iot/windows_iot/restart>`."
msgstr ""
"Aby zapobiec utracie połączenia, ustaw stały adres IP na routerze IoT Box "
