#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:73
msgid ""
"To display margins and costs in the product information window, go to "
"the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Product & PoS categories` section, and enable :guilabel:`Show "
